SANCTUARY
Art by Ikegami Ryouichi
Written by Fumimura Sho
SANCTUARY is a  story about two young men working together to change the shape of Tokyo's
politics - one by becoming a politician, and the other by becoming a Yakuza. Together with their
friendship, determination and will,  they build their own sanctuary.
